author: Justin Wise
title: Wisconsin legislature sues to block enforcement of governor's stay-at-home order
description: The Republican-led Wisconsin legislature is calling on the state's Supreme Court to temporarily block enforcement of Democratic Gov. Tony Evers's stay-at-home order just days after he extended the directive through May 26...
content:
The Republican-led Wisconsin legislature is calling on the state's Supreme Court to temporarily block enforcement of Democratic Gov. Tony Evers's stay-at-home order just days after he extended the directive through May 26.
